Upstream data attribution
-------------------------
The 16 underlying systems were assembled from publicly available primary sources.
Each system's paper.md file lists the upstream data provider (USGS, NIFC, GOES,
FDIC, Compound Labs subgraph, etc.) and date of fetch. Users redistributing the
data are asked to also credit those primary sources where applicable.
